Package com.github.robtimus.obfuscation.annotation

Provides annotations for configuring obfuscators.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ObfuscatorProvider
    A provider for Obfuscators.
    StringRepresentationProvider
    A provider for string representations, that can be used with Obfuscator.obfuscateObject(Object, Supplier).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ObfuscatorFactory
    Utility class that can create Obfuscators from annotations.
    StringRepresentationProvider.BooleanArrayToString
    A string representation provider that uses Arrays.toString(boolean[]), or Object.toString() for other types.
    StringRepresentationProvider.ByteArrayToString
    A string representation provider that uses Arrays.toString(byte[]), or Object.toString() for other types.
    StringRepresentationProvider.CharArrayToString
    A string representation provider that uses Arrays.toString(char[]), or Object.toString() for other types.
    StringRepresentationProvider.DoubleArrayToString
    A string representation provider that uses Arrays.toString(double[]), or Object.toString() for other types.
    StringRepresentationProvider.FloatArrayToString
    A string representation provider that uses Arrays.toString(float[]), or Object.toString() for other types.
    StringRepresentationProvider.IntArrayToString
    A string representation provider that uses Arrays.toString(int[]), or Object.toString() for other types.
    StringRepresentationProvider.LongArrayToString
    A string representation provider that uses Arrays.toString(long[]), or Object.toString() for other types.
    StringRepresentationProvider.ObjectArrayDeepToString
    A string representation provider that uses Arrays.deepToString(Object[]), or Object.toString() for other types.
    StringRepresentationProvider.ObjectArrayToString
    A string representation provider that uses Arrays.toString(Object[]), or Object.toString() for other types.
    StringRepresentationProvider.ShortArrayToString
    A string representation provider that uses Arrays.toString(short[]), or Object.toString() for other types.
    StringRepresentationProvider.ToString
    A string representation provider that uses Object.toString().
    StringRepresentationProvider.TypeSpecific<T>
    A string representation provider that uses specific string representations for a specific type, or Object.toString() for other types.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    ObfuscateAll
    Indicates that obfuscation should be done in a similar way to using Obfuscator.all(char).
    ObfuscateFixedLength
    Indicates that obfuscation should be done in a similar way to using Obfuscator.fixedLength(int, char).
    ObfuscateFixedValue
    Indicates that obfuscation should be done in a similar way to using Obfuscator.fixedValue(String).
    ObfuscateNone
    Indicates that obfuscation should be done in a similar way to using Obfuscator.none().
    ObfuscatePortion
    Indicates that obfuscation should be done in a similar way to using Obfuscator.portion().
    ObfuscateUsing
    Indicates that obfuscation should be done using a custom provided Obfuscator.
    RepresentedBy
    Indicates that objects should get a custom string representation when being obfuscated using Obfuscator.obfuscateObject(Object, Supplier).

Package com.github.robtimus.obfuscation.annotation Description

Provides annotations for configuring obfuscators. Theses annotations can be used by framework-specific processors to apply these obfuscators.
